          "The origins of the largest church in Forodain are clouded by myths and imperilled by conflict. The word of Aeladh is clarified and recorded in the sacred text An B'Aelathil, adhering to the accounts of Blessed Brede, including accurate reproductions of the miracles at Muhr-in-nRos — the spoken word of God himself.",
